{"type": "article", "id": 18519, "title": "你成为手机摄影大师的13个阻碍丨好奇心研究所", "description": "大海啊你都是水，自拍啊都像个鬼。", "date": "2015-12-11T18:00:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3532, "name": "报告"}], "category": 4, "column": 33, "author": 112725, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 165, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153658vuMBTlR8yVPQWckw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t如果拍照是检验感情的唯一标准，好朋友应该就是那个拍照站在你前面比你脸还大的人，男朋友应该就是那个苦练拍照技术把你拍得腿长脸小气质佳的人（当然并没有）。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从按键手机到像素日益精进的智能机，用手机拍照好像成为了一个基本技能。人们对于手机拍照和修图几乎陷入了某种痴迷，<span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/18469.html\">Instagram <span>等照片分享社区已经火到了让人们直接用滤镜给孩子取名的程度。</span></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在本报之前文章中，人们对手机拍照持这些态度：<span><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/17458.html\"><span>老婆痛苦生娃的时候跑过去自拍；</span></a><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/17288.html\"><span>见证婚礼用手机<span>而不是用心；</span></span></a><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/15565.html\"><span>化妆品的研发</span><span>标准要看</span><span>自拍效果好不好；</span></a><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/15287.html\"><span>自拍时无暇顾及危不危险死亡率很高。</span></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t尽管风靡全球，手机拍照这门把妹绝学依然存在 <span>bug</span>。<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/mobs/650.html\"><span>为了</span><span>了解</span><span>爱拍照的所粉对手机拍照还有哪些不满意</span><span>，本报「好奇心研究所」做过一次</span>“<span>你用手机拍照遇到了什么困难？</span>”<span>的投票，我们收获了共</span> 4644 <span>次表态。</span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是人们在拍照的时候经常遇到的困境：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t1.  打算拍照了被提示：您的内存不足，请清空一些内存再拍照。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153644QUG0pCcdHNS67whz.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"272\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>2.  </span>想偷拍，自动开了闪光灯。（尴尬\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153645WNfz4a5BYrA0USge.gif\" width=\"341\" height=\"192\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56304985\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>3.</span><span>  </span>日版的<span>iPhone 6 </span>不能关掉快门声音（连开会的时候偷拍玩游戏的老板都不行了\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153645RqmxlAhPzH4SuUCa.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"250\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>4.  </span>日出开始，我手机卡了。（<span>@ </span>潘小班）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153647HKyS63dMNPGoxOJs.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"305\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.61\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>5. </span><span> 我拍的夜景是：</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/blackafrica\" target=\"_blank\">非洲夜景</a>——冈比亚芭蕾舞学员为竞争黑天鹅角色深夜加练or马拉维青年骑行西藏前后对比。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153649aIOTubZMxYjUrc90.jpg\" width=\"597\" height=\"448\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.75041876\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>6. </span><span> </span>自拍拍不到全身。（@\r\n她说她有她的风格）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021536496NPOxkJAWeXbf8zu.gif\" width=\"636\" height=\"358\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56289308\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>7.  </span>所以，再美的风景自拍也只有大脸。（<span>@ </span>露晨<span>C</span>）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153651qJohV7nj4IF9NwX0.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>8.  </span><span>360 </span>度全死角？怎么都找不到传说中的 <span>361 </span>度！（<span>@ Jaywoo</span>）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153651DAcn0s8Pzx67WTNI.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>9. </span><span> </span>脸大，手短，心累（<span>@ </span>萌萌美）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153652f0jaxUMWe8AH4biQ.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"275\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>10.  </span>自己印象中的自己是美美的，照出来的效果是我想报警。（<span>@ Boney</span>）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153652KmLafwoEM8rC7vIY.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>11.  </span>女友说要拍的白白的、瘦瘦的、腿长长的、脸要像打了玻尿酸一样，于是我变成了前男友。（<span>@ </span>爱在阳光中）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153653A7PQ8YzjgVh4WxdI.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"268\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>12.  </span>不加滤镜等于世上没有美景。（赵少爷）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153656cH0WYyUKhwsQ7AJM.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"278\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.556\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>13.  </span>唉，为什么我不是吴彦祖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153657tgejhBCPfMH5s9bw.jpg\" width=\"1017\" height=\"665\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.65388397\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}